NIgerian Police Force  A housewife in Bagudo Local Government Area of Kebbi State has reportedly killed her husband so that she could go back to her former hubby. According to the police, the suspect, Auta Singe, conspired with one Garba Hassan and Sahabi Garba at Sabon Gari Village, Illo district area of Bagudo to kill her husband, Abdullahi Shaho, to remarry her ex-spouse. Commissioner of Police in the state, Garba Danjuma, confirmed the incident during a briefing with journalists. He said the housewife and the two men conspired with have been arrested.